<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2027] Deprecate Directory.touchFile</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2027</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Lucene doesn&apos;t use this method, and, FindBugs reports that FSDirectory&apos;s impl shouldn&apos;t swallow the returned result from File.setLastModified.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
